#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn17.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn17.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 10. Sagāthakasutta → sagāthasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn17.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Sagāthakasutta "
msgstr "10. With Verses "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.232, sc1
msgctxt "sn17.10:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.10:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … adhigamāya. "
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.10:1.3"
msgid "Idhāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ passāmi sakkārena abhibhūtaṃ pariyādiṇṇacittaṃ, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannaṃ. "
msgstr "Take a case where I see a certain person whose mind is overcome and overwhelmed by honor. When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.10:1.4"
msgid "Idha panāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ passāmi asakkārena abhibhūtaṃ pariyādiṇṇacittaṃ, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannaṃ. "
msgstr "Take another case where I see a certain person whose mind is overcome and overwhelmed by lack of honor. When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.10:1.5"
msgid "Idha panāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ passāmi sakkārena ca asakkārena ca tadubhayena abhibhūtaṃ pariyādiṇṇacittaṃ, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannaṃ. "
msgstr "And take another case where I see a certain person whose mind is overcome and overwhelmed by both honor and lack of honor. When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.10:1.6"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … "
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …” "

msgctxt "sn17.10:1.7"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn17.10:2.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn17.10:2.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā: "
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn17.10:3.1"
msgid "“Yassa sakkariyamānassa, "
msgstr "“Whether they’re honored "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn17.10:3.2"
msgid "asakkārena cūbhayaṃ; "
msgstr "or not honored, or both, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn17.10:3.3"
msgid "Samādhi na vikampati, "
msgstr "their immersion doesn’t waver "

# NOTE: I feel appamada is a better fit here.
#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: appamāṇavihārino → appamādaviharino (pts1-2) | appamādavihārino (mr)
msgctxt "sn17.10:3.4"
msgid "appamāṇavihārino. "
msgstr "as they live diligently. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn17.10:4.1"
msgid "Taṃ jhāyinaṃ sātatikaṃ, "
msgstr "They persistently practice absorption "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn17.10:4.2"
msgid "sukhumaṃ diṭṭhivipassakaṃ; "
msgstr "with subtle view and discernment. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn17.10:4.3"
msgid "Upādānakkhayārāmaṃ, "
msgstr "Rejoicing in the ending of grasping, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn17.10:4.4"
msgid "āhu sappuriso itī”ti. "
msgstr "they’re said to be a good person.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.10:4.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.10:4.6"
msgid "Paṭhamo vaggo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn17.10:5.1"
msgid "Dāruṇo baḷisaṃ kummaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn17.10:5.2"
msgid "dīghalomi ca mīḷhakaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn17.10:5.3"
msgid "Asani diddhaṃ siṅgālaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn17.10:5.4"
msgid "verambhena sagāthakanti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
